title: My Disability Comedy is Not Your “Inspiration Porn” | My Life Online

media:group.media:title: My Disability Comedy is Not Your “Inspiration Porn” | My Life Online
media:group.media:description:
Louie Lingard aka NotLewy hates "inspiration porn" and has garnered millions of followers on TikTok for making crude jokes that make fun of his physical disability. Despite his success, comedy isn't his passion. He wants to be a rapper but when he creates content about his music (and not about his disability) his views plummet. He feels stuck between what the TikTok algorithm wants and what he wants.
